  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump, twirl, and flip your way around a spooky castle! You're a tiny spirit, awoken from your grave to find all your other spirit buds have scattered around the castle grounds. Help get them back home, and unlock the puzzles of this haunted land.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285910/extras/261156e2cfcb9367c3322cf1a7864ba9.poster.avif?t=1732502092\" width=480 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285910/extras/261156e2cfcb9367c3322cf1a7864ba9.webm?t=1732502092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285910/extras/261156e2cfcb9367c3322cf1a7864ba9.mp4?t=1732502092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Design</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smooth, prescise platforming</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lo-fi artstyle & music</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Non-linear exploration</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock doors and find your way around</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect all the lost coins and spirits</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple levels to discover and unlock</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Best played on gamepad!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump, twirl, and flip your way around a spooky castle! You're a tiny spirit, awoken from your grave to find all your other spirit buds have scattered around the castle grounds. Help get them back home, and unlock the puzzles of this haunted land.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285910/extras/261156e2cfcb9367c3322cf1a7864ba9.poster.avif?t=1732502092\" width=480 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285910/extras/261156e2cfcb9367c3322cf1a7864ba9.webm?t=1732502092\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3285910/extras/261156e2cfcb9367c3322cf1a7864ba9.mp4?t=1732502092\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Design</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smooth, prescise platforming</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lo-fi artstyle & music</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Non-linear exploration</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock doors and find your way around</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect all the lost coins and spirits</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple levels to discover and unlock</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Best played on gamepad!</p>",
